QR Capacities

This module contains the capacities and limitations of QR code's number of characters, sizes, number of ECCs, alignment pattern locations, etc, as arrays with values already calculated (known at compiletime).

Imports

qrTypes

Types

QRCapacity[T] = array[QRECLevel, array[QRVersion, T]]
Array made of other 4 arrays, each corresponding to a different QRECLevel and containing 40 values corresponding to each QRVersion.   Source   Edit
